@10xcryptodev 
Did you see #16808 that addressed the same issue?
That pull created some amount of controversy. So other devs' conceptual opinions are needed :)

@za-kk thanks for testing with Qt 5.12
updated the `ku_IQ` to check the version 

IMHO it's better to have this fix until Qt solves all the cases and the codebase moves the minimum Qt version (now is 5.5.1), it's not so easy to bump Qt default versions and the codebase has other fixes like this one

